-- Oil may reach $150 a barrel by July 4: Morgan Stanley
-- 
-- Fri Jun 6, 2008 9:40am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/06/06/businesspro-oil-morganstanley-dc-idUSWLA448520080606

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - Crude oil may reach $150 a barrel by 
July 4, investment bank Morgan Stanley said in a research note 
on Friday, the latest prediction that the market will hit fresh 
record highs. 

  "We are calling for a short-term spike in oil prices," the 
bank said.  (Reporting by  Alex Lawler ; editing by William Hardy)